This is a Flutter WebView starter template. The project structure is complete with all native Android and iOS scaffold files.

IMPORTANT RULES:
1. DO NOT modify AndroidManifest.xml, build.gradle, settings.gradle, MainActivity.kt, or Info.plist
2. DO NOT change the package name or bundle ID - they are already set correctly
3. ONLY modify files inside lib/ directory and assets/
4. The app uses WebView to load web content - keep this architecture
5. All URLs are centralized in lib/constants/app_constants.dart - update only this file for URL changes
6. Placeholders like __APP_NAME__, __PACKAGE_NAME__, __BASE_URL__ have already been replaced - do not reference them

You can:
- Modify lib/ files freely
- Add new screens in lib/screens/
- Add new widgets in lib/widgets/
- Update URLs in lib/constants/app_constants.dart
- Add assets to assets/ folders
- Add new dependencies to pubspec.yaml (non-native only)
